snippet.title: Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Fight #justiceforJohnny
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Fight, turns out Amber Heard is the abuser. I don't like domestic Violence at all, its a dumb situation all around. I think that since it's Johnny depp everyones all ready for justice, which is okay.. I just wish everyone fought for domestic violent cases, not just ones of celebrities. Johnny depp and amber heard divorced a while back, but audio just surfaced of Amber Heard confessing that her and Johnny Depp had an altercation, but Amber actually hit Johnny. But she wasn't "Punching" him so its okay.
I think Johnny deserves justice, but I also think everyone else involved in domestic violence also deserves justice. 

Johnny Depp and Amber Heard FIght : https://theblast.com/110013/fans-demand-justice-for-johnny-depp-after-amber-heard-admits-hit
